definitions.definition: Having multiple facets or ( geometric ) faces .
examples: The diamond had a multifaceted cut.

definitions.definition: Having many aspects ; nuanced or diverse .
examples: Joanne was a multifaceted individual; she knew how to bargain both with Wall Street brokers and push-cart vendors.

main_definition: Having multiple facets or ( geometric ) faces .
secondary_definitions: Having many aspects ; nuanced or diverse .
